Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 12)

Package: file-stage
Architecture: all
Depends: bash, coreutils, util-linux, ${misc:Depends}
Description: stage file copy, move, and symlink operations
 file-stage provides fst, a small shell command for staging cp, mv, and ln
 operations in one directory and applying them later in another directory.
